    "summary": "Comet (Wear Comet) is an Indian lifestyle sneaker brand making elevated everyday sneakers with clean silhouettes, earthy-neutrals and occasional bold colour pops, designed for Indian city life. Their positioning blends comfort and craftsmanship with a confident, expressive attitude summed up in lines like “Never Shy, Never Sorry” and “Designed to Defy,” targeting style‑conscious youth and everyday explorers.",
